abstract: National Assn of Realtors reports slip in April sales of existing homes, largely because there are not enough properties being listed to meet demand.
lead_paragraph: A Realtors group says the April decline occurred because of rising prices and relatively few listings.

headline.print_headline: Rise in Prices Pushes Home Sales Down
